title: Kendra and Holly are Sliding Down the Rabbit Hole
description: This week Claire (@clairethescare) and Ashley (@ashleyhammm) are doing a direct comparison between everything they learned from Kendra (@kendrawilkinson)'s Sliding into Home and Holly (@hollymadison)'s Down the Rabbit Hole.NOTE: This week features a good chunk of Taylor talk and our own life ramblings if you hate that part please skip to approx 18 minutes.
